graph TD
    UserDriver[Driver App (Spanish)] <-->|WebSocket Audio Stream| APIG[AWS API Gateway (WebSocket)]
    UserPassenger[Passenger App (English)] <-->|WebSocket Audio Stream| APIG

    subgraph AWS Cloud
        APIG -->|Route| LambdaHandlers[AWS Lambda Handler]

        LambdaHandlers -->|1. Stream Audio| Transcribe[Amazon Transcribe Streaming]
        Transcribe -->|2. Text (Source)| LambdaLogic[Translation Logic]
        LambdaLogic -->|3. Text (Source)| Translate[Amazon Translate]
        Translate -->|4. Text (Target)| LambdaLogic
        LambdaLogic -->|5. Text (Target)| Polly[Amazon Polly]
        Polly -->|6. Audio (Target)| LambdaHandlers
    end

    LambdaHandlers -->|Return Audio| APIG

    style UserDriver fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style UserPassenger fill:#9ff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style AWS Cloud fill:#eee,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
